amilton Mixtape]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Move You]]\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 2017\n| \u2014{{efn-ua|\"Move You\" peaked at number 58 on the ''Billboard'' [[Digital Songs]] chart, which is a component chart of the ''Billboard'' Hot 100.<ref name=\"SinglesUS\" />}}\n| \u2014{{efn-ua|\"Move You\" peaked at number 181 on the [[UK Singles Downloads Chart|Official UK Singles Downloads Chart]], which is a component chart of the [[UK Singles Chart|Official UK Singles Chart]].<ref name=\"SinglesUK\" />}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''Meaning of Life''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Meaning of Life (Kelly Clarkson song)|Meaning of Life]]\"\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Christmas Eve - Recorded at Spotify Studios NYC\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/1ueZZjEeoThIvgJr4OKKa5|title=Spotify Singles - Holiday by Kelly Clarkson|website=Spotify|accessdate=January 13, 2020}}</ref>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| ''Spotify Singles - Holiday''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I've Loved You Since Forever\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Hoda Kotb]])</span>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n| \u2014{{efn-ua|\"I've Loved You Since Forever\" peaked at number 35 on the ''Billboard'' [[Digital Songs]] chart, which is a component chart of the ''Billboard'' Hot 100.<ref name=\"SinglesUS\" />}}\n| \u2014\n| {{n/a|Non-album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Never Enough\"<ref>{{cite AV media notes|title=[[The Greatest Showman#The Greatest Showman \u2013 Reimagined|The Greatest Showman \u2013 Reimagined]] |others=Various artists |year=2018 |publisher=Atlantic Records/[[Fox Music]]/[[20th Century Fox]] |id=567607-2 |type=booklet}}</ref>\n| \u2014{{efn-ua|\"Never Enough\" peaked at number 14 on the ''Billboard'' Digital Songs chart, which is a component chart of the ''Billboard'' Hot 100.<ref name=\"SinglesUS\" />}}\n| 59\n| ''[[The Greatest Showman: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack#The Greatest Showman: Reimagined|The Greatest Showman: Reimagined]]''\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"font-size:90%\"| 