27/http://www.kellyclarkson.com/us/news/kelly-unveils-stronger-tracklisting |archivedate=September 25, 2011 }}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"RIAA - Jason Aldean\">\n{{cite web |url=http://riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?artist=%22Aldean,%20Jason%22 |title=RIAA \u2014 Searchable Database: Aldean, Jason |work=RIAA Gold & Platinum Awards Program |publisher=Recording Industry Association of America |accessdate=December 28, 2011 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160103171739/http://riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?artist=%22Aldean,%20Jason%22 |archivedate=January 3, 2016 }}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"BillboarHot100Jump\">\n{{cite news| url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2009/01/kelly-clarksons.html |title=Kelly Clarkson's 'My Life' makes history |first=Todd |last=Martens |work=[[Los Angeles Times]] |publisher=[[Tribune Company]] |date=January 29, 2009 |accessdate=June 18, 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"RCA Record Deal\">\n{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2236928.stm|work=[[BBC News]] |publisher=BBC|title=US Pop Idol: Your views|date=October 1, 2002 |accessdate=June 18, 2012 }}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"My December Time feature\">\n{{cite news| url=http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1637584,00.html|work=[[Time (magazine)|Time]] |publisher=[[Time Inc.]]|first=David|last=Browne|title=Kelly Clarkson's Solo Misstep|date=June 26, 2007 |accessdate=June 18, 2012}}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"My December FOX News feature\">\n{{cite news| url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/music/2007-07-23-1116292195_x.htm|work=[[USA Today]] |publisher=[[Gannett Company]]|title=Kelly Clarkson Apologizes to Clive Davis|date=July 23, 2007 |accessdate=June 18, 2012}}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"Breakaway worldwide sales\">\n{{cite news|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/11/21/kelly-clarkson-and-bruno-mars-to-perform-on-the-x-factor-results-show/111378/ |work=[[TV by the Numbers]] |publisher=[[Tribune Media Services]] |title=Kelly Clarkson and Bruno Mars to perf