ire]]\n| ''[[Love Somebody (album)|Love Somebody]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[All I Ask of You]]\"<ref name=\"Song - All I Ask of You\" />\n| [[Josh Groban]]\n| ''[[Stages (Josh Groban album)|Stages]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"The Cry Inside\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/reviews/the-secret-scripture-toronto-review/5109037.article|title='The Secret Scripture': Toronto Review|publisher=}}</ref>\n| 2016\n| {{n/a}}\n| ''[[The Secret Scripture (film)|The Secret Scripture]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Love Goes On\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7669833/tim-mcgraw-kelly-clarkson-lady-antebellum-skillet-the-shack|title=Tim McGraw, Kelly Clarkson, Lady Antebellum, Skillet and More Contribute New Songs to 'The Shack' Soundtrack: Listen|publisher=}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2017\n| [[Aloe Blacc]]\n| ''[[The Shack (2017 film)|The Shack]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Oh Holy Night\" <small>(''Home'' Holiday Version)</small>\n| {{n/a}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Home: Adventures with Tip & Oh|Home for the Holidays]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/home-for-the-holidays-original-soundtrack/1315184238|title=Home for the Holidays (Original Soundtrack) Various Artists|publisher=Apple Music|accessdate=June 10, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Christmas Is a Feeling\"\n| [[Ben Schwartz]] <br /> [[Home: Adventures with Tip & Oh|''Home'' cast]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Grown-Up Christmas List]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.knoxnews.com/story/entertainment/columnists/chuck-campbell/2018/10/24/pentatonix-new-album-christmas-here-martina-mcbride-holiday-season-vnv-nation-noire-review/1701039002/|title=Pentatonix's Christmas album is reliable as Santa; McBride also feels the holiday spirit|last=Campbell|first=Chuck|work=Knox News|date=October 24, 2018|accessdate=October 26, 2018}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n| [[Pentatonix]]\n| ''[[Christmas Is Here!]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Don't Dream It's Over]]\"\n| [[Brynn Cartelli]]\n| ''The Complete Season 14 Collection (The Voice Performance)''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Couldn't Be Better]]\" <small>(Pop version)</small>\n| rowspan=\"7\"| 2019\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n| rowspan=\"6\"| ''[[UglyDolls (soundtrack)|UglyDolls: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Today's the Day\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \t\"Couldn't Be Better\" <small>(Movie version)</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''UglyDolls'' cast\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Today's the (Perfect) Day\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"All Dolled Up\"\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Janelle Mon\u00e1e]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Unbreakable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Tell Me Something I Don't Know\"\n| [[Trisha Yearwood]]\n| ''[[Every Girl (album)|Every Girl]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Born to Die\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2020\n| {{n/a}} \n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Trolls World Tour (soundtrack)|Trolls World Tour: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Just Sing\"\n| [[Justin Timberlake]], [[Anna Kendrick]], [[Mary J. Blige]], [[Anderson Paak]], [[Kenan Thompson]], [[Kunal Nayyar]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Just Sing (Finale)\"\n| Justin Timberlake, Anna Kendrick, [[James Corden]], [[George Clinton (musician)|George Clinton]], Mary J. Blige, Anderson Paak, [[Rachel Bloom]], Kenan Thompson, [[Anthony Ramos (actor)|Anthony Ramos]], [[Red Velvet (band)|Red Velvet]], [[Icona Pop]], [[Sam Rockwell]]\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Kelly Clarkson videography]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{notelist-ua|30em}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em|refs=\n<ref name=\"AlbumsUS\">\n''Billboard'' album chart positions for all singles and tracks:\n* ''Billboard'' 200: {{cite web |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=kelly clarkson|chart=Billboard 200}} |title=Kelly Clarkson Album & Song Chart History: The Billboard 200 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |accessdate=June 18, 2012 }}\n* ''Billboard'' Top Album Sales: {{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/charts/2016-03-26/top-album-sales |title=Top Album Sales |wo