ade Singlet Top 100 |language=French |work=Schweizer Hitparade |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=June 18, 2012 }}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"SinglesUK\">\nOfficial UK Singles chart positions for all singles and tracks:\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/artist/_/kelly%20clarkson/ |title=Kelly Clarkson Singles Discography \u2014 Official UK Charts |work=[[UK Singles Chart|The Official UK Singles Chart]] |publisher=Official Charts Company |accessdate=June 18, 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100724030634/http://www.theofficialcharts.com/artist/_/kelly%20clarkson/ |archivedate=July 24, 2010 }}\nExcept for:\n* \"A Moment Like This\": {{cite web|first=Tobias|last=Zywietz|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/CLUK2006.HTM|title=Chart Log UK \u2014 2006|publisher=Zobbel.de|accessdate=February 2, 2012}}\n* \"Beautiful Disaster\": {{cite web|first=Tobias|last=Zywietz|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/111119cluk.txt|title=Chart Log UK \u2014 Update 19.11.2011|publisher=Zobbel.de|accessdate=February 2, 2012}}\n* \"People Like Us\": {{cite web|first=Tobias|last=Zywietz|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/130629cluk.txt|title=Chart Log UK \u2014 Update 29.06.2013|publisher=Zobbel.de|accessdate=July 10, 2013}}\n* \"Invincible\": {{cite web|first=Tobias|last=Zywietz|url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/150712cluk.txt|title=Chart Log UK \u2014 Update 12.07.2015|publisher=Zobbel.de|accessdate=July 12, 2015}}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"ARIA - Kelly Clarkson Singles\">\nARIA accreditations for singles:\n* \"Miss Independent\": {{Cite certification |region=Australia |type=single |certyear=2003 |accessdate=June 18, 2012 }}\n* \"Low\", \"The Trouble with Love Is\", and \"Breakaway\": {{Cite certification |region=Australia |type=single |certyear=2004 |accessdate=June 18, 2012 }}\n* \"Since U Been Gone\" and \"Because of You\": {{Cite certification |region=Australia |type=single |certyear=2005 |accessdate=June 18, 2012 }}\n* \"Never Again\": {{Cite certification |region=Austral